thread.title_full: Auto Europe Australia reviewed by TKreo

author: TKreo
title: TKreo
text: Very easy to use, and informative website. All the details and extras are displayed up front before payment. Where information cannot be given at time of payment this is then provided within 48 hours of booking. Highly recommended considering the many other confusing options for car hire in Europe. 5 stars.
